    <p>End-to-end encryption ensures your files are always protected.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="feature-icon">
      <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
    </div>
    <h3>Lightning Fast</h3>
    <p>Optimized infrastructure for rapid uploads and downloads.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="feature-icon">
      <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
    </div>
    <h3>Collaborative</h3>
    <p>Easily share files and manage permissions with your team.</p>
  </div>
</div>

